svg.source: Title: How it works participant Client participant Server Client-->Server: Connect Server->Client: Do you wanna play a game? Client->Server: Yes Server->Client: Enter your nickname: Client->Server: Nickname Server->Server: Add new client Server-->Client: Connection established Server->Client: Select one topic Client->Server: choosed topic Server->Server: Add client in topic Server-->Client: Wait for another player Server-->Client: Game starts Server-->Client: Round 1 Server->Client: Client receives image Client->Server: Answer Note right of Client: After 3 Rounds Server->Client: Results
